## How it works

Someone posts a workout in the club Slack with the where, when, and what, and people react with an emoji if they plan to come.

These workouts are informal and not coached. The Thursday track sessions started with one member "wanting to do the speed workouts I would be doing anyways with other people."

When a practice gets cancelled, members often meet at the usual time and place and do the workout anyway.
